### Hadith 1:606

*Narrated 'Aun bin Abi Juhaifa:*

My father said, "I saw Allah's Apostle at a place called Al-Abtah. Bilal
came and informed him about the prayer and then came out with an Anza
and planted it in front of Allah's Apostle at Al-Abtah and pronounced
the Iqama."

